---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const metadata = {
  title: "Privacy Policy - Wortaso",
  description: "Privacy Policy for Wortaso",
};
---

<BaseLayout {metadata}>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground italic mb-10">
      Last updated: 11.04.2026
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4">
      This Privacy Policy describes how your personal information is handled
      when you use the Wortaso mobile application ("the App").
    </p>
    <p class="mb-8">
      By using the App, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy
      Policy.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      I have developed Wortaso as a free educational application for learning
      German articles. The App is provided at no cost and is intended for use
      "as is".
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Protecting your privacy is very important to me. This Privacy Policy
      explains how information is collected, used, and safeguarded when you use
      the App.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">
      2. Data Controller (Contact Information)
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-4">The data controller responsible for this App is:</p>
    <p class="mb-4"><strong>Name: Amin Rashidbeigi</strong></p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy or data
      protection, please contact me using the email below.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">
      3. Information Collection and Use
    </h2>
    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">
      3.1 No Personal Data Collection
    </h3>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The App does not collect, store, transmit, or process any data that can
      personally identify you. As an exception, the App generates a random
      anonymous installation ID (UUID) used solely for referral and promo code
      features — this ID is not linked to your name, email address, Apple ID,
      Google account, or any other personally identifying information. See
      sections 3.5 and 3.6 for details.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-3">Specifically:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
      <li>
        <strong class="text-foreground">No Registration:</strong> You are not required
        to create an account or provide any personal information.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong class="text-foreground"
          >No Analytics or Tracking in the App:</strong
        > The App does not use third-party analytics tools, tracking technologies,
        or monitoring services. The website uses Google Analytics — see Section 3.4
        below.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong class="text-foreground">No Advertising:</strong> The App does not
        display advertisements and does not use advertising identifiers.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong class="text-foreground">No Marketing:</strong> No marketing or profiling
        activities are performed.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">3.2 Local Device Data</h3>
    <p class="mb-3">
      Any learning progress, preferences, or usage data are stored locally on
      your device only. This data:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
      <li>Remains on your device</li>
      <li>Is not transmitted to any server</li>
      <li>Is not accessible to me</li>
      <li>Can be deleted by uninstalling the App</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
      Note: a randomly generated anonymous installation ID may be transmitted to
      our servers in connection with the referral and promo code features — see
      sections 3.5 and 3.6 below.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">3.3 Local Notifications</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The App uses local notifications to provide daily study reminders. These
      notifications are scheduled and triggered entirely on your device. No data
      regarding your notification settings or the timing of these alerts is
      collected by or transmitted to the Developer.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">
      3.4 Website Analytics (Google Analytics)
    </h3>
    <p class="mb-4">
      This website uses Google Analytics 4, a web analytics service provided by
      Google LLC ("Google"). Google Analytics uses cookies to collect anonymous
      usage data, including:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
      <li>Pages visited and time spent on the site</li>
      <li>General geographic region (country/city level)</li>
      <li>Device type and browser</li>
      <li>Referring source (e.g., search engine)</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4">
      IP addresses are anonymized before processing. This data is used solely to
      understand how visitors use the website and to improve its content.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      <strong>Legal basis:</strong> Your explicit consent — Art. 6(1)(a) GDPR. Analytics
      cookies are only placed after you accept the cookie consent banner.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      <strong>Withdraw consent:</strong> You can withdraw your consent at any time
      by clearing your browser's local storage or by declining cookies in the cookie
      banner on your next visit.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      For more information, see Google's Privacy Policy:{" "}
      <a
        href="https://policies.google.com/privacy"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-primary hover:underline"
      >
        https://policies.google.com/privacy
      </a>
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">3.5 Device Identifiers</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">
      When you use Wortaso, the app generates a random installation ID (UUID)
      and stores it locally on your device. This ID is used solely to prevent
      duplicate redemptions of referral and promo codes, and to allow you to
      unlock shared vocabulary lists. It is not linked to your name, email
      address, Apple ID, Google account, or any other personally identifying
      information.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The installation ID is transmitted to our servers (Supabase) when you
      share a vocabulary list or redeem a referral/promo code. It is retained
      for a maximum of 60 days from the date of the referral or redemption,
      after which it is automatically deleted.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">3.6 Referral Feature</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Wortaso includes a "share to unlock" feature. When you share a vocabulary
      list, the app creates an anonymous referral code stored on our servers
      alongside your installation ID and the name of the shared list. No
      personal name, email address, or account data is transmitted or stored as
      part of this process.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      When someone installs the app via your referral link, their installation
      ID is recorded to mark the referral as redeemed. All referral records are
      automatically deleted after 60 days.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">
      3.7 Play Store Attribution (Android only)
    </h3>
    <p class="mb-4">
      On Android, the app reads the Google Play Store install referrer string to
      automatically apply vocabulary list unlocks when you install the app via a
      referral link. This data is read once at first launch and is used only to
      identify the referral code embedded in the install link. No additional
      data is collected from the Play Store attribution API.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">
      4. Third-Party Services (Google Play Store)
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The App is distributed via the Google Play Store. Google may collect
      certain technical and usage-related information in accordance with its own
      privacy practices. This may include:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
      <li>Device information</li>
      <li>Operating system version</li>
      <li>Download statistics</li>
      <li>Performance data</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4">
      I do not receive access to any personally identifiable information
      collected by Google.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      For more information, please review Google's Privacy Policy:<br />
      <a
        href="https://policies.google.com/privacy"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-primary hover:underline"
      >
        https://policies.google.com/privacy
      </a>
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">
      5. Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR)
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      This App is available within the European Union and complies with the
      General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The App processes a limited amount of anonymous technical data
      (installation ID) in connection with the referral and promo code features
      described in sections 3.5 and 3.6. The legal bases for this processing
      are:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 text-muted-foreground">
      <li>
        Article 6(1)(f) GDPR – Legitimate interest in providing a secure,
        functional, and privacy-friendly educational service, including
        preventing duplicate redemptions of referral and promo codes.
      </li>
      <li>
        Article 6(1)(a) GDPR – Your explicit consent for website analytics
        cookies (Google Analytics).
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">6. Your Rights Under GDPR</h2>
    <p class="mb-3">
      Since the App processes a limited amount of anonymous data (installation
      ID), you have the following rights under the GDPR:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
      <li>Right of access (Art. 15 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Right to rectification (Art. 16 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Right to erasure (Art. 17 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Right to restriction of processing (Art. 18 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Right to data portability (Art. 20 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Right to object (Art. 21 GDPR)</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4">
      For the limited data processed (anonymous installation ID, retained for up
      to 60 days), you may exercise these rights by contacting the address
      provided in section 10. In practice, installation ID records are deleted
      automatically within 60 days.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      If you have concerns about data protection, you may contact me using the
      information provided above.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">7. Data Security</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Appropriate technical and organizational measures are taken to ensure that
      the App operates securely and that no unauthorized access to user data
      occurs.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Where data is transmitted to external servers (e.g., the anonymous
      installation ID stored on Supabase), appropriate technical measures are
      applied to prevent unauthorized access. Referral and installation ID
      records are automatically deleted after 60 days.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The App does not knowingly collect personal information from children
      under the age of 13. Since no personal data is collected at all, the App
      complies with applicable child protection and privacy regulations.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      If you believe that a child has provided personal information, please
      contact me immediately.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">
      9. Changes to This Privacy Policy
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time to reflect legal,
      technical, or functional changes.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Any updates will be published within the App and/or on this page. The
      "Last updated" date will be revised accordingly.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      You are encouraged to review this Privacy Policy periodically.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">10. Contact</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      If you have any questions, feedback, or concerns regarding this Privacy
      Policy, please contact:
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Email:</strong>{" "}
      <a href="mailto:wortasoapp@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline"
        >wortasoapp@gmail.com</a
      >
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
